<td id="469AE34831B18F2AA096ABD9BDB6089A" colspan="1" pageId="7" pageNumber="34" rowspan="1">Fruit berry, purple-red, ellipsoid or globose; stem villous, rarely glabrous; petiole puberulent</td>
